who need services can find the appropriate placement and level of care.\r\n\r\nWe hope that our site provides you with the information you need as you search for help for yourself or loved one. I invite you to contact us today with questions or to receive more information on our programs and treatment team.\r\n\r\n<em>Sincerely,</em>\r\n\r\nMichael S. McDonald, Jr.\r\nChief Executive Officer – Managing Director','​CEO Welcome','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-v1','','','2014-12-08 19:57:55','2014-12-08 19:57:55','',33,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/33-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(254,2,'2014-12-08 20:41:04','2014-12-08 20:41:04','','Frequently Asked Questions','','inherit','open','open','','50-revision-v1','','','2014-12-08 20:41:04','2014-12-08 20:41:04','',50,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/50-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(255,2,'2014-12-08 20:44:14','2014-12-08 20:44:14',' ','','','publish','open','open','','255','','','2014-12-11 12:27:32','2014-12-11 17:27:32','',42,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/?p=255',19,'nav_menu_item','',0),(256,2,'2014-12-09 14:54:52','2014-12-09 14:54:52','','ceo-welcome','','inherit','open','open','','ceo-welcome','','','2014-12-09 14:54:52','2014-12-09 14:54:52','',6,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/ceo-welcome.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(257,2,'2014-12-09 14:55:13','2014-12-09 14:55:13','Welcome to Holly Hill Hospital. For over 35 years, the Holly Hill name has been one of comfort and quality and I’m proud to say that we are constantly evolving, growing and enriching our programs to continue in this tradition of providing excellence in clinical behavioral health care.\r\n\r\nIt is our priority at Holly Hill to provide our patients with the treatment and resources needed to return to their communities as healthier individuals. To accomplish this goal I am joined by a team of clinical leaders who are experts in their field and share the vision and passion necessary to provide the best possible programming for the patients in our care. As a community resource, we also provide around the clock, no cost assessments to ensure that those who need services can find the appropriate placement and level of care.\r\n\r\nWe hope that our site provides you with the information you need as you search for help for yourself or loved one. I invite you to contact us today with questions or to receive more information on our programs and treatment team.\r\n\r\n<em>Sincerely,</em>\r\n\r\nMichael S. McDonald, Jr.\r\nChief Executive Officer – Managing Director','​CEO Welcome','','inherit','open','open','','6-revision-v1','','','2014-12-09 14:55:13','2014-12-09 14:55:13','',6,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/6-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(258,2,'2014-12-09 15:11:31','2014-12-09 15:11:31','<p class=\"western\"><a href=\"http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/joint-commission-logo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-260\" src=\"http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/joint-commission-logo.jpg\" alt=\"joint-commission-logo\" width=\"100\" height=\"101\" /></a></p>\n<p class=\"western\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Holly Hill Hospital is fully licensed by the state of North Carolina and is accredited by the Joint Commission.</span></span></span></p>','​Licensing & Accreditation','','inherit','open','open','','11-autosave-v1','','','2014-12-09 15:11:31','2014-12-09 15:11:31','',11,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/11-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(259,2,'2014-12-09 15:02:55','2014-12-09 15:02:55','<p class=\"western\"><img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/themes/hollyhill/assets/images/logo-gold-commission.png\" alt=\"Joint Commission Gold Logo\" width=\"70\" height=\"70\" /></p>\r\n<p clas