.stage.towermarketing.net/54-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(269,2,'2014-12-09 15:53:14','2014-12-09 15:53:14','An outpatient program available to adults ages 18 and over, the Holly Hill Partial Hospitalization Program is designed for those who need more support than traditional, once a week therapy, in treating mental health concerns. Specializing in depressive, anxiety, bipolar and personality disorders, the PHP provides patients with 5 day a week access to a psychiatrist, registered nurse and therapist. The program is from 8:45am – 2:15pm, Monday through Friday and allows patients the freedom to receive intensive medication management and therapeutic services, while being able to return home during nights and weekends.\r\n\r\nThe backbone of the program is psychotherapy groups. These groups allow patients to work on problems simultaneously, receive support and feedback from others with similar problems, and provide real life examples of other patients’ behaviors, all within a safe setting for patients to try out new behaviors.\r\n\r\nGroup therapy topics include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Coping Skills</li>\r\n	<li>Anger Management</li>\r\n	<li>Family Dynamics</li>\r\n	<li>Spirituality</li>\r\n	<li>Healthy Lifestyles</li>\r\n	<li>Communication Skills</li>\r\n	<li>Stress Trigger Identification &amp;  Response</li>\r\n	<li>Grief &amp; Loss</li>\r\n	<li>Stress Management</li>\r\n	<li>Crisis Management Skills</li>\r\n	<li>Trauma Recovery</li>\r\n	<li>Relaxation Therapy</li>\r\n	<li>Planning for Success</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<table style=\"height: 104px;\" border=\"0\" width=\"431\">\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\" colspan=\"2\">To schedule a free intake assessment:</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Monday-Friday</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Evenings and Weekends</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8:00am to 5:00pm</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">919.250.7000</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">919.250.7307</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">800.447.1800</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Adult Outpatient (PHP)','','inherit','open','open','','19-revision-v1','','','2014-12-09 15:53:14','2014-12-09 15:53:14','',19,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/19-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(270,2,'2014-12-09 15:54:29','2014-12-09 15:54:29','','team-Childers','','inherit','open','open','','team-childers','','','2014-12-09 15:54:29','2014-12-09 15:54:29','',0,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/team-Childers.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(271,2,'2014-12-09 15:54:30','2014-12-09 15:54:30','','team-claros','','inherit','open','open','','team-claros','','','2014-12-09 15:54:30','2014-12-09 15:54:30','',0,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/team-claros.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(272,2,'2014-12-09 15:54:31','2014-12-09 15:54:31','','team-cornwall','','inherit','open','open','','team-cornwall','','','2014-12-09 15:54:31','2014-12-09 15:54:31','',0,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/team-cornwall.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(273,2,'2014-12-09 15:54:32','2014-12-09 15:54:32','','team-Gacengeci','','inherit','open','open','','team-gacengeci','','','2014-12-09 15:54:32','2014-12-09 15:54:32','',0,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/team-Gacengeci.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(274,2,'2014-12-09 15:54:33','2014-12-09 15:54:33','','team-jack','','inherit','open','open','','team-jack','','','2014-12-09 15:54:33','2014-12-09 15:54:33','',0,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/team-jack.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(275,2,'2014-12-09 15:54:34','2014-12-09 15:54:34','','team-lincoln','','inherit','open','open','','team-lincoln','','','2014-12-09 15:54:34','2014-12-09 15:54:34','',0,'http://hollyhill.stage