2-22 19:31:28','',45,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(384,2,'2014-12-22 14:32:35','2014-12-22 19:32:35','','20','','inherit','open','open','','20','','','2014-12-22 14:32:35','2014-12-22 19:32:35','',43,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/20.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(385,2,'2014-12-22 14:41:09','2014-12-22 19:41:09','','stock-photo-7887163-bluebell-wood','','inherit','open','open','','stock-photo-7887163-bluebell-wood','','','2014-12-22 14:41:09','2014-12-22 19:41:09','',20,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/stock-photo-7887163-bluebell-wood.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(386,2,'2014-12-22 14:41:14','2014-12-22 19:41:14','','Treatment Trails','','inherit','open','open','','20-revision-v1','','','2014-12-22 14:41:14','2014-12-22 19:41:14','',20,'http://hollyhill.stage.towermarketing.net/20-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(387,2,'2014-12-22 14:41:40','2014-12-22 19:41:40','Join the team of Holly Hill Hospital, a growing, private, psychiatric facility that has provided over 30 years’ worth of quality care and recovery services to the community. Based in Raleigh, NC, Holly Hill Hospital is perfectly located in a rapidly growing family-oriented community that is just hours from the mountains and the beaches and is a surrounded by major universities. We are privileged to have a rich compliment of dedicated employees.\r\n\r\nHolly Hill Hospital offers competitive compensation and excellent benefits including medical, dental, vision, life, 401K with matching, voluntary supplemental benefits, tuition reimbursement, and paid time off.\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"https://uhs.ats.hrsmart.com/cgi-bin/portal/alljobs.cgi?qty=25&amp;order=jobtitle&amp;companycode=544\" name=\"Holly Hill Hospital Career Opportunities\" width=\"100%\" height=\"600\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"1\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"yes\"></iframe